  }}
>
  <article class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 dark:prose-invert">
    <h1>About PraveenTechWorld</h1>
    <p>
      PraveenTechWorld is a practical technology knowledge base. We help students,
      office workers, knowledge workers, and creators use technology more
      effectively.
    </p>
    <h2>Who I Am</h2>
    <p>
      My name is Praveen. I'm a technology enthusiast who has spent years
      troubleshooting, building, and writing about the tools and systems that
      power our digital lives. This site is my way of sharing what I have learned
      and making it easier for others to navigate an increasingly complex
      technology landscape.
    </p>
    <p>
      I believe technology should serve people, not the other way around. Every
      guide on this site comes from real experience, real testing, and a genuine
      desire to help you get things done faster.
    </p>
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Write practical guides you can use today</li>
      <li>Test AI tools and workflows</li>
      <li>Solve common Windows and Android problems</li>
      <li>Help you improve productivity with technology</li>
      <li>Show you how to use AI for career growth</li>
      <li>Review free software alternatives to expensive tools</li>
      <li>Guide you through website setup and search engine indexing</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      No fluff. No filler. No AI-generated spam. Every piece of content on this
      site is written to help you save time, solve problems, or learn something
      useful. I do not chase trends or write about things I have not personally
      tested.
    </p>
    <h2>Why This Site Exists</h2>
    <p>
      Most technology content falls into two camps, overly technical guides that
      assume you already know the jargon, and surface-level listicles that leave
      you without a working solution. PraveenTechWorld bridges that gap with
      step-by-step guides that actually work, written for real people solving
      real problems.
    </p>
